title: "Chowk" means a fully or partially enclosed space permanently open to the sky within a building at any level; inner chowk being enclosed on all sides and an outer chowk having one unenclosed side
clause_text: "Chowk" means a fully or partially enclosed space permanently open to the sky within a building at any level; inner chowk being enclosed on all sides and an outer chowk having one unenclosed side.
